name: Dee Bailey
text: A really nice store that has a lot of different materials.The salespeople are really helpful as well.

name: stormi boddie
text: Great resource for parents that are involved in there kids learning and development. I found games that helped my son read instantly at the age of 4. It taught me that I put in the work but just needed to find a way to reach him.

name: Terri Lane Robertson
text: A teacher's heaven.  I could lose hours in here.  Everything you could think of wanting,  and a few you haven't thought of. Friendly staff.  Clean and organized.

name: Angie Dunham
text: I love visiting this store! They are consistently friendly and helpful. Not only do they immediately know where to find what you're looking for, they will lead the way. If they don't have what you're looking for they will let you know what store to find it.

name: Tamara Williams
text: The staff is knowledgeable and friendly. A great group of women eager to assist teachers in any way. Thank you ladies for all your support.

name: Elizabeth Hanna
text: Great resource not just for teachers, but parents looking for developmental activities or materials to do at home!

name: Live Laugh Love
text: It had everything a child could use to get to the next grade level. I bought comprehensive books, alphabet & number posters.

name: Fee Johnson
text: Received some lamination down for a poster board. Good job. It looks good.

name: Trish Dyess
text: Mr Milligan is one of the most friendliest people to deal with. We have been ordering our graduation supplies from them for over 13 years... When something has went wrong they always have taken care of it.

name: john kinsey
text: Always have find these people to be helpful and ready to meet our needs - if there has ever been an oversight they wen the extra mile to make it right - we have used them for over 15 years

name: Linda Sullivan
text: I have always found everything that I have needed and wanted. Their prices are very reasonable and the staff are very helpful. Keep up the good work!

name: Von
text: I really like this place. It reminds me a little bit of a store on Il that I went to when I stayed there. I plan on making a monthly trip over to this store. One of the things that I love is that they have biblical items for learning too.

name: Monica G
text: Great products, good prices and customer service. They have everything you can think of for teachers, homeschool families and therapists. Definitely worth checking out!

name: Elizabeth Mckay
text:
Items on sale or discontinued  items should be marked  and made clear  to customers that there are no refunds when purchasing.
When I returned an item ,I was told that it was a discontinued item in which I was not aware of before purchasing so I could not exchange or receive money back ;however the store has  a great variety of products.

name: Kurt Frazier
text: So many choices to pick from.  Great bargains for teachers.  Very friendly and helpful staff.  I will be going there often. 📚📚
